data.description: [Call the listing agent Owen at 720-260-2838 for a private showing] Gorgeous Remodeled Home! Upon entering you will be met with beautiful hardwoods in the living room that extend to 2 of the bedrooms on the main floor. The kitchen is a chef's delight featuring ample new cabinets, granite counter-tops, tile floor, and stainless steel appliances. There is a third spacious bedroom off the kitchen that has a new stranded bamboo floor and which could alternately also serve as a dining room and family room. The full bathroom has been beautifully remodeled and has tile floors/walls. There is a large covered patio that is perfect for entertaining. Large private backyard. Newer Furnace (5 years) and Water Heater (5 years). Close to a Park, Shops, Restaurants, and major roads. Welcome Home!
